<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Architect | Atlas AI</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
</html>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <main class="dashboard-container">
    <header class="page-header flex-header">
      <div>
        <h2 style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px">
          Atlas
          <span
            class="badge blue-badge"
            style="font-size: 12px; transform: translateY(-2px)"
            >v1.0</span
          >
        </h2>
        <p class="subtitle">
          Predictive intelligence and wealth optimization engine.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="header-actions">
        <div
          class="sync-badge"
          style="background-color: #111827; color: white; border-color: #374151"
        >
          <span class="sync-dot" style="color: #10b981">●</span> Neural Core
          Online
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="metrics-grid grid-2-1">
      <div
        class="content-card chat-container"
        style="padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 600px"
      >
        <div
          style="
            padding: 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
          "
        >
          <h3 class="section-title title-sm">Active Session</h3>
          <button class="icon-btn">⟳ Clear Context</button>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-history">
          <div class="chat-message atlas-msg">
            <div class="chat-avatar atlas-avatar">A</div>
            <div class="chat-bubble atlas-bubble">
              <p>
                Good afternoon. I've analyzed your recent transaction batch from
                Investec. I detected a
                <strong>14% increase in dining expenses</strong> compared to
                your 30-day moving average.
              </p>
              <p style="margin-top: 8px">
                Would you like me to adjust your upcoming EasyEquities
                allocation to compensate, or ignore this anomaly?
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="chat-message user-msg">
            <div class="chat-bubble user-bubble">
              <p>
                Ignore it for now. But run a projection on what happens if I
                increase my ZAR portfolio contributions by R1,500 next month.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="chat-message atlas-msg">
            <div class="chat-avatar atlas-avatar">A</div>
            <div class="chat-bubble atlas-bubble typing-indicator">
              <span></span><span></span><span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chat-input-area">
          <input
            type="text"
            class="chat-input"
            placeholder="Ask Atlas to analyze your data..."
          />
          <button class="chat-send-btn">Send</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px">
        <div class="content-card">
          <h3 class="section-title title-sm mb-16">Active ML Models</h3>

          <div class="model-status-item">
            <div
              style="
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-between;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
              "
            >
              <span class="tx-title">Transaction Classification</span>
              <span class="text-positive text-sm" style="font-weight: 700"
                >99.2%</span
              >
            </div>
            <div class="progress-track" style="height: 4px">
              <div class="progress-fill fill-blue" style="width: 99.2%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="model-status-item mt-16">
            <div
              style="
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-between;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
              "
            >
              <span class="tx-title">Anomaly Detection (Isolation Forest)</span>
              <span class="text-positive text-sm" style="font-weight: 700"
                >Running</span
              >
            </div>
            <div class="progress-track" style="height: 4px">
              <div
                class="progress-fill"
                style="width: 100%; background-color: #10b981"
              ></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-card" style="flex: 1">
          <h3 class="section-title title-sm mb-16">Discovered Insights</h3>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <span class="insight-icon">💡</span>
            <div>
              <p class="tx-title">Optimization Opportunity</p>
              <p class="tx-subtitle mt-8">
                Rebalancing your Luno wallet back to 15% of your total net worth
                could reduce portfolio volatility by 3.4% based on historical
                data.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card mt-16">
            <span class="insight-icon">⚠️</span>
            <div>
              <p class="tx-title">Subscription Creep</p>
              <p class="tx-subtitle mt-8">
                I found 2 unused SaaS subscriptions in your last 90 days of
                transactions totaling R 450/mo.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
